(287, 'A person turned on the computer without a keyboard plugged in.When she turns on the computer', 'A person turned on the computer without a keyboard plugged in. When she turns on the computer, the computer finds out that there is no keyboard attached and it gives a Keyboard Error message. She then asks Why did it give me a keyboard error? There isn\'t even a keyboard attached?', NULL, 0, 0, '2020-12-31 22:00:00', '2021-01-10 15:09:46'),
(288, 'While trying to diagnose a problem over the phone I told the user to type out his autoexec.bat f', 'While trying to diagnose a problem over the phone I told the user to type out his autoexec. bat file. He said it said File not found. I told him to do a dir. I asked him if he saw autoexec. bat listed. He said, Well it says autoexec, then there\'s some spaces, but no dot, and then it says bat. I said type this in type autoexec. bat. Again he got File not found. I asked him to tell me exactly what he typed. He said, I typed just what you told me: `type autoexecdotbat\'.', NULL, 0, 0, '2020-12-31 22:00:00', '2021-01-10 15:09:46'),
