(567, 'I\'d love you to stay the night, but I\'m afraid you\'ll have to make your own bed. Oh, that\'s', 'I\'d love you to stay the night, but I\'m afraid you\'ll have to make your own bed. Oh, that\'s all right, I don\'t mind at all. Right. Here\'s a hammer, a saw, and some nails. The wood\'s in the garage. I have four legs, but only one foot. What am I? A bed', NULL, 0, 0, '2020-12-31 22:00:00', '2021-01-10 15:09:46'),
