(828, 'One day a guy was driving with his 4-year-old daughterand beeped his car horn by mistake.She t', 'One day a guy was driving with his 4-year-old daughterand beeped his car horn by mistake. She turned and looked at him for an explanation. He said, I did that by accident. She replied, I know that, daddy. He replied, How\'d you know? The girl said, Because you didn\'t say \'ASSHOLE!\' afterwards!', NULL, 0, 0, '2020-12-31 22:00:00', '2021-01-10 15:09:46'),
(829, 'After spending 3-1/2 hours enduring the long lines, surly clerks, andinsane regulations at the', 'After spending 3-1/2 hours enduring the long lines, surly clerks, andinsane regulations at the department of motor vehicles, I stopped at atoy store to pick up a gift for my son. I brought my selection - a baseball bat - to the cash register. Cash or charge? the clerk asked. Cash, I snapped. Then, apologizing for my rudeness, I explained, I\'ve spent the afternoon at the motor-vehicle bureau. Shall I giftwrap the bat? the clerk asked sweetly. Or are you goingback there?', NULL, 0, 0, '2020-12-31 22:00:00', '2021-01-10 15:09:46'),
