(842, 'Where\'s the car? asked Professor Delbert\'s wife when he got home. Did I take it out? \r', 'Where\'s the car? asked Professor Delbert\'s wife when he got home. Did I take it out? Yes, you drove it to school this morning. I suppose you\'re right, my dear. I remember now that after I got out, I turned to thank the man who gave me a lift and wondered where he\'d gone.', NULL, 0, 0, '2020-12-31 22:00:00', '2021-01-10 15:09:46'),
