(2710, 'A business man who has flown to Cape Town from Johannesburg for a meeting misses his flight back h', 'A business man who has flown to Cape Town from Johannesburg for a meeting misses his flight back home. Inquiring, he finds that no other flights are available until the day after tomorrow. As he has to get back to Johannesburg for his wife\'s birthday he decides to rent a car and drive part way, sleep over in the Karoo and then drive the rest of the way the next day. As he is driving through the Karroo and while the sun starting to set he decides he must look for a place to sleep over. After a while he sees a sign saying accommodation available and he turns off the main road and into a dirt road leading into wheat fields on either side with a farm house far ahead in the distance. As he is making his way through the wheat field he is suddenly forced to break as he sees the strangest sight emerging out of the wheat on the right hand side of the road. With car stopped and stalled and dust swirling all around from the skid marks he cannot believe what he is seeing. It appears to be a pig strapped to a wheel chair. But on closer inspection he makes out that the pig is missing its right leg, a paw missing from the elbow joint, an ear and it also has a number of bandages wrapped around parts of its body. With the other left paw, closest to him he notices that this is tied to the wheel chair wheel with wire and using this contraption the pig is able to move the wheel chair. In amazement the businessman sees the pig move slowly across the dirt road in front of his car and then disappear into the wheat field on his left. Finally he collects himself and starts the car again and drives to the farmhouse. On arrival he is met by the farmer. Getting out the farmer asks him if he is here for the room. He says yes but cannot help himself by asking what was that pig on the wheel chair. The farmer at first does not want to answer. But after the business man nags him for an answer he finally agrees but says it is a bit of a long story. He says you know that is an amazing pig! A while ago I was ploughing my fields and it was a very hot day. I became drowsy and fell asleep and then fell off my tractor. Stunned I realized that the tractor had not stopped and I was lying in the way of the plough it was pulling but was unable to move. The blades were getting closer and closer to me and they would have chopped me to bits but suddenly the pig you saw arrived and grabbed my shirt by the collar and he pulled me to safety, just in time! The business man asks: Is that what happened to the pig. Did he get hurt trying to save you!? No says the farmer. You do not understand! Let me explain further... A while ago my wife was making butter in the barn over there. Unfortunately, a part of the dress she was wearing got caught in the cogs of the churning machine and as the cogs turned her dress was being pulled into the mechanism and she was getting closer and closer to the sharp rotating blades that churn the butter. Then just before she got hurt that pig you saw showed up and grabbed her dress and pulled her out of the cogs, saving her. The business man asks: Is that what happened to the pig. Did he get hurt trying to save you!? No says the farmer. You do not understand! Let me explain further... A while ago my young son was playing up on that hill over there next to our water reservoir. He slipped and started to slide down a water drain and was fast moving towards some rusty blades that channel the water. For sure he would have been chopped to bits. But before this could happen that pig you saw showed up and grabbed his shirt by the collar and dragged him to safety. The business man asks: Is that what happened to the pig. Did he get hurt trying to save you!? No says the farmer. You do not understand! with a pig as amazing as this... you simply cannot eat it up all at once.', NULL, 0, 0, '2020-12-31 22:00:00', '2021-01-13 04:30:27'),
